No. 31,

Orig.

Utah v. United States. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 391 U. S. 962.]

Report of Special Master received and ordered filed. Exceptions, if any, may be filed by the parties within 45 days. Reply briefs, if any, may be filed within 30 days thereafter.

Mr. Justice Marshall took no part in the consideration or decision of this matter.
